==Tailoring==
Maple Syrup can be used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] to create the {{name|Floppy Beanie|class=inline}}. It can be used in [[dyeing]], serving as an orange dye at the dye pots, located in [[Emily]]'s and [[Haley]]'s house, [[2 Willow Lane]].

==Quests==
*One Maple Syrup is required to complete the [[Quests#Strange Note|"Strange Note" quest]] that is triggered by reading [[Secret Notes#Secret Note #23|Secret Note #23]].
*One or two Maple Syrup may be requested by several fish in [[Fish Pond#Quests|Fish Pond quests]].

